": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@melbourneaquarium.com.au\", \"value\": \"info@melbourneaquarium.com.au\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+61399235999\", \"value\": \"+61 3 9923 5999\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.visitsealife.com/melbourne/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=yext&utm_content=2\", \"value\": \"www.visitsealife.com/melbourne/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=yext&utm_content=2\"}}','Melbourne Aquarium is wheelchair accessible, with elevators providing access to all levels. Accessible restrooms are available, and assistance is offered for visitors with disabilities; please inquire at guest services for specific needs.','Spring and Autumn offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds compared to peak summer and winter periods.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Explore the wonders of the underwater world at Melbourne Aquarium. Discover diverse marine life from penguins to sharks. Immerse yourself in interactive exhibits and captivating displays.',120,'[\"See the King and Gentoo penguins at the Penguin Playground.\", \"Walk through the underwater tunnels of the Oceanarium.\", \"Encounter sharks, rays, and other marine creatures in the Coral Atoll.\", \"Learn about conservation efforts at the interactive exhibits.\", \"Visit the Mermaid Garden with colorful fish and coral.\", \"Explore the unique seahorse exhibit.\", \"Get up close with the saltwater crocodiles.\", \"Enjoy the daily feeding presentations and talks.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:21','2025-12-12 10:11:21'),(13,13,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:zoo@zoo.org.au\", \"value\": \"zoo@zoo.org.au\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+611300966784\", \"value\": \"+61 1300 966 784\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.zoo.org.au/melbourne\", \"value\": \"www.zoo.org.au/melbourne\"}}','Melbourne Zoo is committed to accessibility. The zoo offers wheelchair rentals, accessible restrooms, and mostly flat pathways, with ramps and elevators available where necessary to ensure access to various exhibits and facilities.','Spring and Autumn offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds than Summer.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Melbourne Zoo is a captivating zoological garden in Melbourne, Australia. Home to over 3,000 animals from around the world, it offers immersive exhibits and conservation programs. It\'s a beloved destination for families, nature enthusiasts, and anyone seeking a connection with wildlife.',240,'[\"See the Orangutans in their innovative, arboreal habitat.\", \"Explore the Trail of the Elephants to learn about these magnificent creatures.\", \"Discover native Australian wildlife in the Australian Bush exhibit.\", \"Marvel at the playful penguins in the Penguin Plaza.\", \"Immerse yourself in the world of primates at the Gorilla Rainforest.\", \"Learn about conservation efforts and the zoo\'s commitment to sustainability.\", \"Attend a Keeper Talk to gain insights into animal behavior and care.\", \"Visit the Butterfly House and wander among hundreds of colourful butterflies.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:28','2025-12-12 10:11:28'),(14,14,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@jungleisland.com\", \"value\": \"info@jungleisland.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+13054007000\", \"value\": \"+1 305-400-7000\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.jungleisland.com/\", \"value\": \"www.jungleisland.com\"}}','Jungle Island offers wheelchair accessibility throughout most of the park. Accessible restrooms and designated parking spaces are available. Some shows and experiences may have limited accessibility, so it\'s recommended to inquire in advance.','Winter','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}]','Jungle Island is an interactive zoological park in Miami, Florida. Home to a variety of exotic animals and engaging shows, it offers an immersive wildlife experience. Explore lush landscapes and connect with fascinating creatures.',180,'[\"Meet the diverse population of parrots and other birds in the Manu Aviary.\", \"Witness the Winged Wonders show featuring free-flying birds.\", \"Observe the Australian red kangaroo and other marsupials.\", \"Explore the reptile collection including crocodiles and snakes.\", \"Engage with lemurs and other primates in interactive experiences.\", \"Enjoy the panoramic views of Miami from various park locations.\", \"Attend educational presentations about animal conservation efforts.\", \"Visit the Penguin Encounter and learn about these amazing birds.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:34','2025-12-12 10:11:34'),(15,15,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@junglequeen.com\", \"value\": \"info@junglequeen.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+19544625596\", \"value\": \"+1 954-462-5596\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.junglequeen.com/\", \"value\": \"www.junglequeen.com\"}}','The Jungle Queen Riverboat and its facilities are partially wheelchair accessible. The main decks are accessible, and accessible restrooms are available. Assistance may be required for boarding depending on the tide levels.','Winter (December - February)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}]','Experience a classic Fort Lauderdale sightseeing cruise aboard the iconic Jungle Queen Riverboat. Enjoy narrated tours of the \'Venice of America\' and scenic views of Millionaire\'s Row. Opt for a Dinner Cruise with an island-themed show.',180,'[\"Narrated sightseeing cruise along the Intracoastal Waterway.\", \"Views of opulent mansions on Millionaire\'s Row.\", \"Explore the tropical isle during the dinner cruise stopover.\", \"Enjoy the all-you-can-eat BBQ ribs and shrimp dinner.\", \"Watch the hilarious and entertaining island-themed show.\", \"Sunset viewing opportunities during evening cruises.\", \"Photo opportunities with the Jungle Queen Riverboat.\", \"Learn about the history and landmarks of Fort Lauderdale.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:41','2025-12-12 10:11:41'),(16,16,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@lioncountrysafari.com\", \"value\": \"info@lioncountrysafari.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+15617931084\", \"value\": \"+1 561-793-1084\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.lioncountrysafari.com/\", \"value\": \"www.lioncountrysafari.com\"}}','Lion Country Safari offers wheelchair accessibility throughout the drive-through preserve and walk-through amusement park. Accessible restrooms are available, and designated parking spaces are provided. Please check their website for specific details regarding ride accessibility.','Winter/Spring','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Lion Country Safari is a drive-through wildlife preserve and amusement park. Encounter hundreds of animals roaming freely in open habitats. It\'s a unique and immersive safari experience.',300,'[\"Drive through the wildlife preserve and see lions, giraffes, rhinos, and zebras up close.\", \"Visit Safari World, the walk-through amusement park.\", \"Enjoy the giraffe feeding experience.\", \"See a wildlife show or demonstration.\", \"Cool off at the water sprayground (seasonal).\", \"Ride the carousel or other amusement park rides.\", \"Observe the various bird species in the aviary.\", \"Grab a bite to eat at one of the restaurants.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:47','2025-12-12 10:11:47'),(17,17,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:musee.catacombes@paris.fr\", \"value\": \"musee.catacombes@paris.fr\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33143224763\", \"value\": \"+33 1 43 22 47 63\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.catacombes.paris.fr/\", \"value\": \"www.catacombes.paris.fr\"}}','The Catacombs are unfortunately not accessible to visitors with reduced mobility due to the presence of many steps. There are no elevators or ramps available. Due to the nature of the site, accessible restrooms are not available.','Spring and Fall offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds than the summer months.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": true, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}]','The Paris Catacombs are an underground ossuary in Paris, France, holding the remains of more than six million people in a small part of a tunnel network. Opened in the late 18th century, they offer a unique and haunting glimpse into the city\'s history. It\'s a truly unforgettable experience.',60,'[\"See the wall of skulls and bones arranged in decorative patterns.\", \"Learn about the history of the Catacombs and why they were created.\", \"Explore the underground tunnels that stretch for miles beneath Paris.\", \"Discover the various chambers and ossuaries within the Catacombs.\", \"Reflect on the sheer number of people whose remains are housed here.\", \"Take photos of the most striking and memorable displays.\", \"Observe the inscriptions and quotes found throughout the site.\", \"Consider the geological history of the limestone quarries that formed the Catacombs.\"]','2025-12-12 10:11:54','2025-12-12 10:11:54'),(18,18,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:contact@parczoologiquedeparis.fr\", \"value\": \"contact@parczoologiquedeparis.fr\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33144752000\", \"value\": \"+33 1 44 75 20 00\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.parczoologiquedeparis.fr/\", \"value\": \"www.parczoologiquedeparis.fr\"}}','The Paris Zoological Park is mostly wheelchair accessible. Elevators are available in the Grand Rocher to access different viewing levels. Accessible restrooms are located throughout the park.','Spring and Summer','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','The Paris Zoological Park, also known as the Vincennes Zoo, is a modern zoo exhibiting animals in their natural habitats. Explore diverse biomes from Patagonia to the Sahel-Sudan. It\'s home to over 2,000 animals.',240,'[\"The Great Rock, an artificial mountain with panoramic views.\", \"The Sahel-Sudan zone, featuring giraffes, lions, and ostriches.\", \"The Patagonia zone, home to penguins and pumas.\", \"The Guyana zone, showcasing rainforest animals like jaguars and manatees.\", \"The Europe zone, highlighting native European species.\", \"Observe the diverse birdlife in the aviary.\", \"Attend animal feeding sessions and educational talks.\", \"Explore the reptile house and discover fascinating reptiles and amphibians.\"]','2025-12-12 10:12:01','2025-12-12 10:12:01'),(19,19,'{\"email\": {\"url\": null, \"value\": null}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33155258210\", \"value\": \"+33 1 55 25 82 10\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.paris.fr/dossiers/bienvenue-au-cimetiere-du-pere-lachaise-47/\", \"value\": \"www.paris.fr/dossiers/bienvenue-au-cimetiere-du-pere-lachaise-47\"}}','Père Lachaise has limited accessibility for visitors with reduced mobility. While some main paths are paved, many are uneven or have steps. Ramps are limited, and elevators are not available. Accessible restrooms are available near the main entrance at Boulevard de Ménilmontant.','Spring and Fall offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds than summer.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}]','Père Lachaise Cemetery is Paris\'s largest cemetery and one of the most famous in the world. It\'s a serene garden space and the final resting place of numerous celebrated figures. Explore its art, history, and peaceful atmosphere.',120,'[\"Tomb of Jim Morrison\", \"Tomb of Oscar Wilde\", \"Tomb of Édith Piaf\", \"Grave of Frédéric Chopin\", \"Grave of Marcel Proust\", \"Grave of Gertrude Stein\", \"Tomb of Yves Montand and Simone Signoret\", \"Explore the unique architectural styles of the tombs and monuments\"]','2025-12-12 10:12:08','2025-12-12 10:12:08');
