INSERT INTO `tips` VALUES (1,1,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings and keep belongings secure within Amaze Amsterdam, especially in crowded areas and dark installations. ','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(2,1,'SAFETY','Amaze Amsterdam can be overwhelming with its intense sensory experiences. Take breaks if needed and don\'t hesitate to exit an installation if you feel uncomfortable or disoriented. Know the location of emergency exits.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(3,1,'SAFETY','If you\'re visiting Amaze Amsterdam solo, let someone know your itinerary and check in with them periodically. Share your location if possible, and be mindful of your phone battery.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(4,1,'SAFETY','Stick to well-lit and populated areas within Amaze Amsterdam, especially if visiting at night. Avoid wandering off on your own and be aware of potential hazards like uneven flooring or low lighting.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(5,1,'SAFETY','If offered assistance by strangers inside Amaze Amsterdam, be cautious and verify their credentials with Amaze staff before accepting help. Trust your instincts.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(6,1,'SAFETY','Be mindful of the legal status of certain substances in Amsterdam, even within tourist attractions like Amaze. Avoid purchasing or consuming illegal drugs, as penalties can be severe.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(7,1,'INSIDER','Book your Amaze Amsterdam tickets online in advance to avoid long queues, especially during peak season.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(8,1,'INSIDER','Check for student or group discounts when purchasing Amaze Amsterdam tickets for potential savings.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(9,1,'INSIDER','Allow at least 2-3 hours to fully experience Amaze Amsterdam. Rushing through the installations will diminish the overall experience. Take your time to immerse yourself.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(10,1,'INSIDER','Consider visiting Amaze Amsterdam during off-peak hours (early mornings or weekdays) to avoid crowds and have a more relaxed and intimate experience with the exhibits.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(11,1,'INSIDER','Charge your phone before visiting Amaze Amsterdam. You\'ll want it for photos and videos, and potentially for navigation or communication if you get separated from your group.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(12,1,'INSIDER','Check the Amaze Amsterdam website for any special events, temporary exhibits, or performances that might be happening during your visit. These can enhance your experience.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(13,1,'INSIDER','Utilize the free Wi-Fi at Amaze Amsterdam to share your experiences on social media or to access information about the exhibits. Consider downloading the Amaze app if they have one.','Reddit (Amaze Amsterdam)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:11:46'),(14,2,'SAFETY','Watch your belongings closely during boarding and disembarking the canal cruise, as crowded areas can be targets for pickpockets.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(15,2,'SAFETY','Be mindful of the edge of the canals, especially when taking photos. Accidents can happen quickly if you\'re not paying attention, particularly after dark or if you\'ve had a few drinks.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(16,2,'SAFETY','If you\'re on an open-top boat, use sunscreen and stay hydrated, especially during sunny days. The sun reflecting off the water can make you burn faster than you realize.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(17,2,'SAFETY','If traveling with children, keep a close eye on them near the water. Ensure they understand the importance of staying seated during the cruise and not leaning over the edge.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(18,2,'SAFETY','Be aware of other boats and canal traffic. Though rare, collisions can occur. Pay attention to the captain\'s instructions and any safety announcements.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(19,2,'SAFETY','If you\'re taking a night cruise, be mindful of your surroundings when you disembark. Stick to well-lit areas and avoid walking alone in unfamiliar neighborhoods.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(20,2,'INSIDER','Opt for a smaller boat tour for a more intimate experience and to navigate narrower canals.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(21,2,'INSIDER','Consider a cruise that includes live commentary for a richer historical context.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(22,2,'INSIDER','Check for combination tickets that bundle a canal cruise with other Amsterdam attractions. This can save you money and time compared to buying tickets separately. Look for deals online or through tourist information centers.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(23,2,'INSIDER','Go early in the morning or later in the evening to avoid the biggest crowds. The canals are especially beautiful during sunrise and sunset, offering fantastic photo opportunities with fewer people around.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(24,2,'INSIDER','Bring snacks and drinks, especially on longer cruises. While some tours offer refreshments, bringing your own can save you money and ensure you have what you like on hand. Check the tour\'s policy on outside food and beverages beforehand.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(25,2,'INSIDER','If visiting during peak season, book your canal cruise tickets in advance online to secure your preferred time slot and avoid long queues. Popular tours can sell out quickly, especially during holidays and weekends.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(26,2,'INSIDER','Choose a cruise that focuses on a specific theme or area of interest. Some tours highlight the city\'s history, while others focus on architecture or specific neighborhoods. This can make your experience more personalized and engaging.','Reddit (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:12:31'),(27,3,'SAFETY','Be aware of sudden loud noises and startling effects; those with sensory sensitivities or heart conditions should consider this before entering.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(28,3,'SAFETY','The Amsterdam Dungeon features dark and confined spaces, so exercise caution when moving, especially in dimly lit areas, to avoid trips or falls. Pay attention to the path.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(29,3,'SAFETY','Actors will interact with the audience. Be prepared for physical contact, though it should be appropriate. Report anything that makes you uncomfortable to staff immediately.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(30,3,'SAFETY','Keep a close watch on your belongings at all times during the show, especially in crowded areas, as pickpockets can operate even inside attractions. Use secure bags.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(31,3,'SAFETY','If you have any medical conditions or phobias (e.g., claustrophobia, fear of blood), inform the Dungeon staff before entering. They can offer advice or alternative routes.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(32,3,'SAFETY','Stick with your group during the tour to avoid getting separated in the dimly lit environment. It can be disorienting to be alone amidst the performances.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(33,3,'INSIDER','Book your tickets online in advance to skip potentially long queues, especially during peak tourist season.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(34,3,'INSIDER','Go on a weekday or during off-peak hours (early morning or late afternoon) for a less crowded experience.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(35,3,'INSIDER','Be prepared to participate! The actors feed off the audience\'s energy, so don\'t be afraid to engage and embrace the immersive experience to get the most out of it. It\'s more fun if you\'re involved.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(36,3,'INSIDER','The Amsterdam Dungeon is not suitable for very young children due to its scary themes and loud noises. Consider the age and sensitivity of your group before visiting. Many adults find it unsettling too.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(37,3,'INSIDER','Check for combo tickets that include other attractions in Amsterdam. This can save you money if you plan to visit multiple sites, so compare options before you buy.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(38,3,'INSIDER','Allow ample time for your visit, as the tour takes around 80 minutes. Factor in waiting time, especially during busy periods. Don\'t rush through, enjoy each scene.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(39,3,'INSIDER','Photos and videos might be restricted in certain areas of the Dungeon, so pay attention to the staff\'s instructions. Respect the rules, so you can fully absorb what\'s in front of you.','Reddit (Amsterdam Dungeon)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:15'),(40,4,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings, especially at night. The narrow, winding closes can be poorly lit and disorienting, making you vulnerable.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(41,4,'SAFETY','Stick to well-lit and populated areas, especially along the Royal Mile, at night. Avoid wandering alone down dark closes (narrow alleyways) late in the evening.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(42,4,'SAFETY','Be mindful of uneven cobblestone streets, especially after rain or in the winter when they can become slippery. Wear sturdy shoes with good grip.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(43,4,'SAFETY','Keep your valuables secure and be aware of pickpockets, particularly in crowded tourist areas like the Royal Mile and around Edinburgh Castle.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(44,4,'SAFETY','If you\'re planning on doing any ghost tours that go into the underground vaults, make sure the company is reputable and has proper safety measures in place. Research reviews beforehand.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(45,4,'SAFETY','Be cautious of the \'prank\' shops selling gag items. Some are quite aggressive in trying to get you to interact, and it can be overwhelming, especially for solo travelers.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(46,4,'INSIDER','Escape the Royal Mile crowds by exploring the closes. Some offer amazing views and a glimpse into the Old Town\'s hidden history.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(47,4,'INSIDER','Look beyond the tourist shops; independent boutiques and artisan shops are tucked away on the side streets.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:13:51'),(48,4,'INSIDER','Consider taking a free walking tour of the Old Town, but remember to tip your guide if you enjoyed it. It\'s a great way to get an overview and learn about the history.','Reddit (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction',1,'