FETY','If visiting during an event or ceremony, be prepared for larger crowds and potential security checks. Arrive early and follow instructions from staff.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(58,5,'SAFETY','In winter, icy conditions can make the grounds slippery. Take extra care walking around the Palace and Abbey ruins, especially early in the morning or late in the afternoon.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(59,5,'INSIDER','Book your tickets online in advance, especially during peak season, to skip the potentially long queues.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(60,5,'INSIDER','Consider visiting Holyrood Palace in the late afternoon for fewer crowds and a more relaxed experience.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(61,5,'INSIDER','Don\'t skip the audio guide included with your ticket. It provides valuable context and enhances the experience as you explore the Palace and Abbey ruins at your own pace.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(62,5,'INSIDER','Allow ample time to explore not just the Palace interior, but also the extensive grounds, gardens and the atmospheric Holyrood Abbey ruins. The gardens can be a lovely escape from the crowds.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(63,5,'INSIDER','Check the Holyrood Palace website for special events, exhibitions, or guided tours that may coincide with your visit. These can offer a unique perspective on the Palace\'s history and significance.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(64,5,'INSIDER','Combine your visit to Holyrood Palace with a walk up Arthur\'s Seat for panoramic views of Edinburgh. The Palace is conveniently located at the foot of the hill.','Reddit (Holyrood Palace)','attraction',1,'2025-12-12 10:14:25'),(65,5,'INSIDER','Photography restrictions may apply inside the Palace. Check with staff o